###############################
# NeutrinoCMS 0.1-beta README #
###############################

Thank you for trying out NeutrinoCMS!

For a list of changes in this release, please read the CHANGELOG file.

Please send your comments and suggestions to <neutrinocms[at]gmail.com>

###########
# CREDITS #
###########

NeutrinoCMS is using the following code (in random order):

	* Markdown Extra *
		A text-to-HTML conversion tool for web writers
		Copyright (c) 2004-2007 Michel Fortin
		<http://www.michelf.com/projects/php-markdown/>

	* Original Markdown
		Copyright (c) 2004-2006 John Gruber
		<http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/>

	* PhpCaptcha *
		A visual and audio CAPTCHA generation library
		Copyright (c) 2005-2006, Edward Eliot
		<http://www.ejeliot.com/pages/2>

	* Polymorphic Behavior *
		Allow the model to be associated with any other model object
		Copyright (c) Andy Dawson (AD7six)
		<http://bakery.cakephp.org/articles/view/polymorphic-behavior>

	* Sluggable Behavior *
		Model behavior to support generation of slugs for models
		Copyright (c) Mariano Iglesias
		<http://cake-syrup.sourceforge.net/ingredients/sluggable-behavior/>

	* google-code-prettify *
		Syntax highlighting of code snippets in a web page
		Copyright (c) Mike Samuel?
		<http://code.google.com/p/google-code-prettify/>

	* Shadowbox *
		A media-viewer script for web pages that allows content to be
		viewed without navigating away from the original linking page
		Copyright (c) 2007 Michael J. I. Jackson
		<http://www.mjijackson.com/shadowbox/>

	* Starbox *
		Starbox allows you to easily create all kinds of rating boxes
		using just one PNG image
		Copyright (c) 2007 Nick Stakenburg
		<http://www.nickstakenburg.com/projects/starbox/>

	* App Helper url caching *
		AppHelper speed improvement tweak for cake reverse routing
		Copyright (c) 2009 Matt Curry
		http://github.com/mcurry/url_cache

	* Wizard component *
		Handles multi-step form navigation, data persistence,
		validation callbacks, and plot-branching navigation.
		Copyright (c) jaredhoyt AT gmail DOT com

If I forgot to mention anyone in the credits,
please e-mail me and I will update it in the next release.


